aho madīyam ityādi padmam iti varāṅgam | vidhāneneti padmāntargatasavyavāmapārśvavartinyor nāḍyor nirnakhamadhyamātarjanyaṅgulidvayena jihvayā vā cālanena etena prajñāyāḥ kṣaraṇaṃ bhavati | tataḥ padmarandhraṃ snigdhaṃ bhavati | tato vajrāgrāṃ taddravena spṛṣṭam atīva paramaṃ sukhaṃ saṃpādayatīti bhāvaḥ | siddhīti mahāsukham ||
